  "intent": "Transfer 50\u00b5L of sample from 1.5mL tubes to corresponding wells in a 96-well aluminum block plate using P300 pipette with 10\u00b5L air gap. Add 50\u00b5L denaturing solution to each sample well with 5x mixing at 50\u00b5L volume. Add 10\u00b5L DTT using P20 pipette to each sample well. Incubate samples at 50\u00b0C for 60 minutes on temperature module, then cool to 4\u00b0C for storage.",
